<T>__{wipe to:}
<L>__{interior high school gym night}
<B>__{medium close shot}
<A>__{at one end of the room an orchestra is playing. george wends his way through the dancing couples toward a supper table. he and harry are carrying plates and pies.}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{here you are.}
<A>__{several of the boys take the plates from him. george looks at them, feeling very grown up and out of place.}
<C>__{harry}
<P>__{(introducing george)}
<D>__{you know my kid brother, george. i'm going to put him through college.}
<A>__{sam wainwright comes in behind harry, waggles his hands at his ears as he talks.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{here comes george. hello, hee haw!}
<A>__{george swings around, delighted to hear a familiar voice.}
<B>__{wider angle}
<A>__{including sam and marty hatch. sam is assured and breezy, wearing very collegiate clothes.}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{oh, oh. sam wainwright! how are you? when did you get here?}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{oh, this afternoon. i thought i'd give the kids a treat.}
