<D>__{dance with her, will you?}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{oh... me? oh, well, i feel funny enough already, with all these kids.}
<C>__{marty}
<D>__{aw, come on. be a sport. just dance with her one time and you'll give her the thrill of her life.}
