<A>__{still staring at george, and smiling.}
<C>__{freddie's voice}
<D>__{...but i couldn't find out. nobody'd ever tell you whoever it was because they'd be scared. they know...}
<B>__{medium closeup}
<A>__{mary and freddie. marty comes into scene, followed by george.}
<C>__{freddie}
<D>__{...what kind of...}
