<A>__{harry on the orchestra platform, whistle in hand.}
<C>__{harry}
<D>__{oyez oyez oyez... the big charleston contest. the prize? a genuine loving cup. those not tapped by the judges will remain on the floor. let's go!}
<B>__{closeup george and mary}
